Project Bureau — ATF1504AS Logic Block D Macrocells

Project Bureau aims at documenting the bitstream format of Microchip ATF15xx CPLDs. This is a work in progress. See more in the repository

Macrocell Configuration Bitmap

Logic block D uses 368 (known) fuses within range 30720..32640 for macrocells MC49, MC50, MC51, MC52, MC53, MC54, MC55, MC56, MC57, MC58, MC59, MC60, MC61, MC62, MC63, MC64.
